title: 'Are You Insane?': Nvidia Founder And CEO Jensen Huang Reportedly Questions Managers Using Less AI
description: At a time when artificial intelligence is rapidly seeping into the workforce ecosystem, Nvidia CEO Jensen Huang has criticised managers that promote the culture of using less AI at work, reports Fortune. “My understanding is that Nvidia has some managers who are telling their people to use less AI. Are you insane?” said Huang during the company's meeting after the Q3 earnings.
